description: Barcelona OntheGo is a new, mobile street food concept in Latin cuisine serving Orange County, CA.We combine wholesome, traditional Latin recipes with modern cooking techniques and local products to bring unsurpassed quality and taste to our customers.Barcelona OntheGo was launched in February 2010 and was one of the pioneer gourmet food trucks in Orange County, CA.We combine wholesome, traditional Spanish recipes with Latin influences, modern cooking techniques, and local products to bring unsurpassed quality and taste to our customers.This unmatched value is the result of a business concept based on the ability to bring the best dish to your work and home, and agility to adapt our menu on the seasonality of products. This assures the freshest and highest quality ingredients and delivers incredible value.One of the most refined Orange County food trucks!
name: Barcelona OntheGo
